{"tid":1762868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：警方在理大事件中克制 是政府及警方努力的成果","createTime":"2019-11-30T02:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T10:18:23.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f59730ec9cc752b9ace9452d727a5548963e34","tid":1762868,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"警方昨日解封理工大學交還校方管理。教育局局長楊潤雄在本台節目《星期六問責》形容是一個<span style=\"color: red;\">安心的結局</span>，沒有發生嚴重受傷的情況，強調政府一直以來都想和平解決事件，指今次事件是社會很多人，包括政府及警方、努力的成果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於警方圍封理大校園的做法，楊潤雄認為警方有責任維持治安、保障生命及財產安全，指警方在事件中克制，盡最大努力希望在校園內的人自願走出來</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，今次事件對整個專上界別都有影響，不單在硬件上的損失，提早結束學期亦影響大專生的學習，而外地生、內地生等都有部分擔心人身安全而離開。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，教育局會主動聯絡各間大學，視乎需要提供協助。他提到大學可以考慮在日常管理上是否能做得更多，舉例指不少大學校園都開放予所有人，是否應考慮如何做到平衡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495259-20191130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495259-20191130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY8mKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=a8a82ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495259-20191130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a333134e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495259-20191130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6fc6091b84d78abd4764dcd16f24e672443b52fd","tid":1762868,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5105bc1da102220e15d07aaa4be0bd46213414","tid":1762868,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"咁姐係用返曱甴對待手足既方式對待佢既仔女都好克制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c